Day 25: Manage the Sprint, Not the Team!
🎯 Manage the sprint, let the team manage themselves!  
👉 Tip: Focus on keeping the sprint on track, not micromanaging tasks. Empower the team to self-organize.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How often do you manage the sprint and allow the team to self-organize?"  
1. Always! 💪  
2. Most of the time 🔄  
3. Could do better 🔧  
4. I tend to manage tasks 🙈
